SubjectTrois-Rivières Port Authority Borrowing Limit ** Increase **
PrecisOrder approving the Supplementary Letters Patent provisions Amending Article 9 of the Letters Patent issued to the Trois-Rivières Port Authority to increase from $13,000,000 to $42,000,000 for the purpose of increasing the aggregate limit on its power to borrow money on its credit for port purposes.
